From Mario Veraart Subject Re Help Importing EPS files into Word jburke writes I was wondering if anyone knew how to view a EPS in Ms Word a Here are the first couple of lines if it helps PS Adobe Creator ProWrite Title TCWN Orientation Portrait Pages PageOrder Ascend Can any one Help James Burke By reading this you agree not to hold the writer responsible for any evil happening that may befall you at any time We had a similar problem in converting a EPS file The solution was simple We changed the first line from PS Adobe to PS Adobe This fouled the converter, the EPS file only contained very simple move and draw statements Mario Mario Veraart TNO Physics and Electronics Laboratory email The Hague The Netherlands If all else fails, show pretty pictures and animated videos, and don't talk about performance , David Bailey